<br>
They have fleshy noses and webbed feet (like us). Proboscis monkeys have only started on the road to semi-aquatic evolution. Large animals not all that dissimilar to Humans and Chimpanzees before they diverged. We left this environment about 5 to 10 million years ago. What kind of creatures we find in the universe can only be guessed at.<br>
Saying that &quot;they&quot; would probably have this or that technology is assuming a lot. Our methods of mathematical calculation might also be Alien to them. That and our Physical Laws of the Universe. All revised and corrected frequently. Even having experiments that support a theory is not absolute proof of its accuracy. As we keep finding out, a theory may fit the evidence but be entirely wrong. For a long time it was a fact that the Sun revolved around the Earth. For most day to day applications this idea worked but it was still wrong. Aliens might also operate on false pemises that suffice. Religions even. <br>
